WEBVTT

00:03.291 --> 00:05.083
♪ OHHH OHHH OHHH ♪

00:08.083 --> 00:09.917
I CAN'T TAKE ANYMORE.

00:09.959 --> 00:11.583
(Pete) Uh-huh.

00:11.625 --> 00:14.375
I JUST CAME BACK FROM A RUN
ON THE BEACH ALONE.

00:14.417 --> 00:15.834
I HAD LUNCH ALONE.

00:15.875 --> 00:18.166
I RAN MY ERRANDS
OVER THE WEEKEND ALONE.

00:18.208 --> 00:20.625
IT IS WHAT IT IS.

00:20.667 --> 00:24.250
WHAT DOES THAT EVEN MEAN?
I WANT MY FRIEND BACK.

00:24.291 --> 00:26.625
WELL, THAT COULD BE TOUGH,
THE WAY YOU SANDBAGGED HER.

00:26.667 --> 00:28.625
WE HAVE TO FIX THIS.

00:28.667 --> 00:31.750
MAYBE...

00:31.792 --> 00:36.041
MAYBE SAM AND NAOMI
SHOULD WORK TOGETHER.

00:36.083 --> 00:38.000
MAYBE THAT'S THE ANSWER.

00:38.041 --> 00:40.875
MAYBE IT IS WHAT IT IS.

00:40.917 --> 00:43.417
YOU KNOW WHAT? THERE'S
SOMETHING WRONG WITH YOU.

00:43.458 --> 00:45.959
I'M CALLING VIOLET.
NO, DON'T--DON'T CALL VIOLET.

00:46.000 --> 00:47.875
HELLO?
WE HAVE TO DO SOMETHING.

00:47.917 --> 00:49.625
TONIGHT?
ABOUT SAM AND NAOMI.

00:49.667 --> 00:52.000
THERE'S NOTHING TO DO.
ARE--ARE YOU WITH PETE?

00:52.041 --> 00:53.625
CONFERENCE CALL.

00:53.667 --> 00:56.625
REMEMBER THE GOOD OLD DAYS--
SAM AND NAOMI TOGETHER,

00:56.667 --> 00:58.625
THE PRACTICE
RUNNING IN HARMONY?

00:58.667 --> 01:00.709
YOU--YOU DIDN'T
WORK HERE THEN.
THAT'S NOT THE POINT.

01:00.750 --> 01:03.709
THE POINT IS WE MUST RETURN
TO THE WAY IT WAS.

01:03.750 --> 01:06.875
DAYS OF YESTERYEAR? BAD IDEA.
NO, NO, ACTUALLY,
IT'S A--IT'S A GREAT IDEA.

01:06.917 --> 01:09.625
Hold on.
I'm gonna get Coop.
NO, DON'T GET COOP.

01:09.667 --> 01:11.375
(telephone rings)

01:11.417 --> 01:13.041
HOW COME I DIDN'T KNOW

01:13.083 --> 01:15.083
ANY NAUGHTY SCHOOLGIRLS
IN HIGH SCHOOL?
I DID.

01:15.125 --> 01:17.667
PETE, ARE YOU AT VIOLET'S?
NO. TECHNOLOGY.
CONFERENCE CALL.

01:17.709 --> 01:19.166
WE'RE DOING
AN INTERVENTION.

01:19.208 --> 01:22.250
ENDING THE WAR--SAM AND NAOMI,
PEACE AT THE OFFICE.

01:22.291 --> 01:24.792
OH, I'M IN.
I'M NOT GETTING INVOLVED,
PEOPLE.

01:24.834 --> 01:26.834
WE ARE GONNA PUT THEM
IN A ROOM

01:26.875 --> 01:29.333
AND CREATE A SUPPORTIVE,
NONTHREATENING ENVIRONMENT.

01:29.375 --> 01:32.875
I NEED SOMEONE
TO LICK MY LOLLIPOP.
I GOTTA GO.

01:32.917 --> 01:34.917
D-DON'T HANG UP.
(doorbell ringing)

01:34.959 --> 01:36.917
ARE--ARE WE AGREED?
YEP, TOMORROW,
FIRST THING--

01:36.959 --> 01:38.917
OPERATION "GET NAOMI AND SAM
BACK TOGETHER."

01:38.959 --> 01:41.333
I GOTTA GO.
UH, KEVIN'S HERE.

01:41.375 --> 01:44.291
IF YOU HANG UP,
DOES THAT MEAN--
(dial tone drones)

01:44.333 --> 01:45.500
HEY.

01:45.542 --> 01:47.500
CHINESE TAKEOUT,
BOTTLE OF WINE,

01:47.542 --> 01:49.500
FANCY SUBTITLED MOVIE,
HOT ACTION MOVIE--

01:49.542 --> 01:51.500
WHICHEVER YOU NEED
TO BE HAPPY.

01:51.542 --> 01:55.125
THIS IS EXACTLY
WHAT I NEED.

01:55.166 --> 01:58.333
♪♪

01:58.375 --> 02:00.375
HOW DO YOU FEEL
ABOUT RULES?

02:00.417 --> 02:03.375
YOU THINK WE SHOULD SET RULES
FOR NAOMI AND SAM?

02:03.417 --> 02:05.041
NO, NO.
RULES ABOUT DATING.

02:05.083 --> 02:07.125
SEX RULES?
MM-HMM, YES, THAT'S RIGHT.

02:07.166 --> 02:10.125
IS THIS YOU
TRYING TO BOND WITH ME?
NO, I'M SEEKING
YOUR PROFESSIONAL OPINION.

02:10.166 --> 02:12.125
I'M THINKING ABOUT SETTING
SOME RULES FOR MYSELF.

02:12.166 --> 02:14.709
IS THIS ABOUT
THE S.W.A.T. GUY?
MM-HMM.

02:14.750 --> 02:16.750
YOU TWO HAVEN'T...
NOPE.

02:16.792 --> 02:18.917
WOW. YOU'RE ONE OF
THOSE WOMEN.

02:18.959 --> 02:20.917
I'M NOT ONE OF THOSE WOMEN.

02:20.959 --> 02:22.917
I'M CAUTIOUS.
I'M TRYING TO BE CAUTIOUS.

02:22.959 --> 02:24.458
SO YOU DON'T LIKE HIM?

02:24.500 --> 02:27.709
I DO LIKE HIM. I JUST...
ONCE YOU SLEEP WITH SOMEONE--

02:27.750 --> 02:29.500
I DON'T KNOW, IN THE PAST,
I-I MESSED UP.

02:29.542 --> 02:32.291
I JUST DON'T WANT TO
DO THAT AGAIN, SO I THOUGHT

02:32.333 --> 02:34.542
IF I MADE SOME RULES--
BUT YOU WANT
TO SLEEP WITH HIM?

02:34.583 --> 02:36.542
YES, BUT MY RULES, I--
WHAT RULES?

02:36.583 --> 02:39.000
YOU NEED TO SEE
A THERAPIST.

02:39.041 --> 02:41.041
THERAPISTS ARE OVERRATED.
UH...

02:41.083 --> 02:44.208
OKAY, JUST SAW 'EM IN THE LOBBY.
THEY'RE ON THE WAY UP.
TOGETHER? THAT'S A GOOD SIGN.

02:44.250 --> 02:46.291
YEAH, BUT THEY'RE
NOT TALKING AT ALL.
WELL, THAT'S A BAD SIGN.

02:46.333 --> 02:50.041
HEY, YOU'RE BACK.
I AM, I AM, FULL-TIME
AS OF TODAY. OKAY, OKAY.

02:50.083 --> 02:52.333
SEE? BACK TO THE WAY
IT WAS.
(elevator bell dings)

02:55.000 --> 02:57.917
ALL RIGHT, BE STRONG,
BE FIRM

02:57.959 --> 03:00.041
AND DON'T TAKE NO
FOR AN ANSWER.

03:00.083 --> 03:02.417
I THOUGHT WE SAID
NO MORE SECRET MEETINGS.

03:02.458 --> 03:04.500
IT'S NOT SECRET.
WHOSE CUPCAKES?

03:04.542 --> 03:06.583
WHAT IS THIS?
IT'S AN INTERVENTION.

03:06.625 --> 03:09.250
SOMEBODY HAVE A PROBLEM
THAT I'M NOT AWARE OF?

03:09.291 --> 03:11.583
OH, NO, NO, NO. IT'S FOR YOU,
FOR BOTH OF YOU.

03:11.625 --> 03:14.125
TO GET YOU TWO BACK...

03:14.166 --> 03:16.375
TO THE WAY IT USED TO BE--

03:16.417 --> 03:18.583
OUR LEADERS, TOGETHER.

03:18.625 --> 03:21.333
NO.
NO, THAT'S--
THAT'S NOT GONNA HAPPEN.

03:21.375 --> 03:22.792
SORRY.

03:26.083 --> 03:28.542
OKAY, I WAS BEING POLITE.

03:28.583 --> 03:31.000
THAT IS EXACTLY
WHAT IS GOING TO HAPPEN.

03:31.041 --> 03:33.000
WE CANCELED
YOUR MORNING PATIENTS.

03:33.041 --> 03:35.834
YOU TWO ARE GONNA SIT
IN THIS ROOM,

03:35.875 --> 03:37.834
YOU'RE GONNA EAT THE CUPCAKES,
AND YOU'RE GONNA REMEMBER

03:37.875 --> 03:40.041
WHY IT IS THAT YOU STARTED
THIS PRACTICE

03:40.083 --> 03:42.375
IN THE FIRST PLACE TOGETHER.

03:42.417 --> 03:45.375
AND THEN YOU ARE GOING TO AGREE
ON A WAY TO MOVE FORWARD,

03:45.417 --> 03:48.041
WITH THIS PRACTICE,
TOGETHER AS A FAMILY.

03:48.083 --> 03:50.291
DON'T COME OUT
UNTIL YOU'RE DONE.

04:00.750 --> 04:03.917
(woman) BRADEN DOESN'T SPEAK,
DOESN'T UNDERSTAND WHEN I DO.

04:03.959 --> 04:05.792
WE'VE BEEN TO FIVE DOCTORS.

04:05.834 --> 04:08.625
MY FRIEND BETH SAID YOU WERE
AMAZING WITH HER DAUGHTER.

04:08.667 --> 04:10.625
CHECK THIS OUT.
LOOK AT THAT.

04:10.667 --> 04:14.208
IT'S GOT A LADDER.
IT'S GOT A LITTLE GUY IN THERE.

04:14.250 --> 04:16.709
HMM?

04:26.291 --> 04:28.709
PLEASE DON'T JUST TELL ME
HE'S AUTISTIC.

04:28.750 --> 04:31.667
BRADEN MIGHT BE PROCESSING
MORE THAN YOU THINK,

04:31.709 --> 04:33.875
AND IF HE IS--
AUGMENTATIVE
COMMUNICATION THERAPY,

04:33.917 --> 04:37.750
SENSORY INTEGRATION PROGRAMS--
THEY HAVEN'T WORKED FOR HIM.

04:37.792 --> 04:41.458
SO HE STARTED SPEAKING
AND... HE JUST STOPPED AT 4?

04:41.500 --> 04:43.458
SO NOW YOU SAY
IT COULD BE ENVIRONMENTAL,

04:43.500 --> 04:46.083
IT COULD BE GENETIC,
IT COULD BE ANYTHING.

04:46.125 --> 04:47.583
SOMETIMES KIDS
JUST BECOME AUTISTIC.

04:47.625 --> 04:49.583
UNFORTUNATELY, IT'S ONE OF
THOSE DISORDERS

04:49.625 --> 04:52.333
THAT JUST ISN'T
THAT WELL UNDERSTOOD.

04:55.625 --> 04:57.500
YOU KNOW, YOU LOOK FAMILIAR.

04:57.542 --> 05:00.667
DO WE KNOW EACH OTHER
FROM SOMEWHERE?
DO WE?

05:00.709 --> 05:05.333
I DON'T KNOW.
MAYBE I JUST WANT TO KNOW YOU.

05:05.375 --> 05:07.709
SO YOU'LL DO SOMETHING
FOR BRADEN.

05:07.750 --> 05:10.709
I'LL TAKE A LOOK,
I'LL SEE WHAT WE CAN FIND,

05:10.750 --> 05:14.500
AND I WILL DO WHAT I CAN.
I PROMISE.
OKAY.

05:17.083 --> 05:18.792
HEY, BRADEN.

05:18.834 --> 05:21.166
CAN YOU FOLLOW
THE LIGHT FOR ME?

05:25.083 --> 05:27.750
CAN YOU LOOK UP?

05:27.792 --> 05:29.166
WHOA.

05:29.208 --> 05:31.458
HERE. THERE YOU GO.

05:39.959 --> 05:41.458
HI.

05:53.083 --> 05:55.834
IT'S WORKING, NAYSAYER.

05:55.875 --> 05:57.375
IT IS WHAT IT IS.

05:57.417 --> 05:59.375
WHAT DOES THAT
EVEN MEAN?

05:59.417 --> 06:01.625
YOU THINK WE'RE BACK?

06:01.667 --> 06:04.000
I THINK WE MIGHT BE BACK.

06:04.041 --> 06:06.542
HEY, WELL, WE AGREE.

06:06.583 --> 06:09.041
YOU SEE?
WE'RE ALL GONNA VOTE...

06:09.083 --> 06:10.834
MY WAY OR NAOMI'S.

06:10.875 --> 06:14.041
WHAT? NO.
YOU CHOOSE WHICH ONE OF US
RUNS THE PRACTICE.

06:14.083 --> 06:16.125
AND WE'LL ABIDE BY
THE DECISION.

06:16.166 --> 06:19.000
THIS IS A BAD IDEA.
THIS IS GONNA TEAR US APART.
I WARNED YOU.

06:19.041 --> 06:20.542
LOOK, YOU WERE RIGHT.

06:20.583 --> 06:22.625
WE CAN'T KEEP ON THE WAY
THINGS HAVE BEEN GOING.

06:22.667 --> 06:24.792
SO WE WILL CAMPAIGN FAIRLY.
RIGHT, NO DIRTY TRICKS,
NO BRIBERY.

06:24.834 --> 06:28.041
CIVIL, DEMOCRATIC--THE WAY
THE PRACTICE SHOULD BE RUN.

06:28.083 --> 06:30.667
ARE YOU SUGGESTING THAT
I WANT ANYTHING ELSE?

06:30.709 --> 06:33.667
DO I GET A VOTE? I MEAN,
I AM PART OF THE PRACTICE.

06:33.709 --> 06:35.500
THAT WAS THE DEAL, RIGHT?
YEAH, OF COURSE YOU ARE.

06:35.542 --> 06:38.667
RIGHT. I-I WOULDN'T HAVE IT
ANY OTHER WAY.

06:38.709 --> 06:40.667
SO, UH, TOMORROW
AT THE CLOSE OF BUSINESS.

06:40.709 --> 06:43.417
RIGHT.
WE VOTE... TOMORROW.

06:43.458 --> 06:44.875
ALL RIGHT?

06:44.917 --> 06:46.208
(chuckles)

06:54.125 --> 06:56.583
SO SEEING AS YOU'RE
GONNA NEED VOTES,

06:56.625 --> 06:58.375
I WANT TO START SHADOWING.

06:58.417 --> 07:00.041
I DON'T HAVE YOUR VOTE?

07:00.083 --> 07:02.667
AFTER I BULLIED SAM
INTO TAKING YOU BACK?

07:02.709 --> 07:05.041
YOU WERE THE REASON
THAT I LEFT.

07:05.083 --> 07:08.250
YOU'RE DOING A GAMETE
MICROMANIPULATION ON FRIDAY.

07:08.291 --> 07:09.709
I WANT TO ASSIST.

07:09.750 --> 07:11.250
OH, UH, THE COLES.

07:11.291 --> 07:14.125
UM, THAT'S--THAT'S DIFFICULT.
IT IS WHAT YOU PROMISED.

07:14.166 --> 07:17.709
I NEED TO GET THE HOURS FOR
MY MIDWIFE CERTIFICATION.
I KNOW.

07:17.750 --> 07:20.875
IT'S JUST THAT THE COLES, UH,
CAN BE A LITTLE BIT JUMPY.

07:20.917 --> 07:22.875
SO LET ME
THINK ABOUT IT, OKAY?

07:22.917 --> 07:25.166
YOU THINK ABOUT IT.
VOTE'S TOMORROW.

07:27.083 --> 07:29.500
SHARB--
SHARBAT QALZAI?

07:29.542 --> 07:32.500
I AM SHARBAT'S FATHER,
IDREES QALZAI.

07:32.542 --> 07:34.750
HELLO. HOW DO YOU DO?
I'M DR. MONTGOMERY.

07:34.792 --> 07:36.458
SHARBAT IDENTIFIED YOU

07:36.500 --> 07:39.041
AS THE TOP DOCTOR
THERE IS FOR LADIES.

07:39.083 --> 07:41.500
I WOULD LIKE FOR YOU
TO GIVE HER THE EXAM

07:41.542 --> 07:43.500
YOU GIVE
YOUR VERY BEST PATIENTS.

07:43.542 --> 07:47.041
ALL OF MY PATIENTS
GET THE VERY BEST,

07:47.083 --> 07:49.041
AND SHARBAT WILL BE
NO EXCEPTION.

07:49.083 --> 07:52.625
SO WHY DON'T, UH,
WHY DON'T YOU COME BACK?

07:56.542 --> 07:58.250
(whispers)
STAY RIGHT HERE.

07:58.291 --> 07:59.792
OH, HEY. I'M NOT GONNA--

07:59.834 --> 08:02.709
I'M NOT GONNA KNOW ANYTHING
TILL I GET HIS LABS BACK.

08:02.750 --> 08:04.750
I REMEMBER
WHERE I KNOW YOU FROM.
NICOLE?

08:04.792 --> 08:08.166
YOU'RE THE ONE IN THE PICTURES,
NAKED, ON THAT WEB SITE.
WHAT?

08:08.208 --> 08:10.625
THE DATING SITE
FOR ADULTS.

08:10.667 --> 08:12.834
YOU SAW THAT?

08:12.875 --> 08:14.959
YOU ARE A DOCTOR,
A PEDIATRICIAN--

08:15.000 --> 08:17.750
PLEASE, NICOLE--
HOW CAN YOU WORK
WITH CHILDREN?

08:17.792 --> 08:19.750
OKAY, THAT SITE
HAS NOTHING TO...

08:19.792 --> 08:23.583
MY PERSONAL LIFE DOES NOT IMPACT
THE CARE I GIVE MY PATIENTS.

08:23.625 --> 08:25.792
HOW CAN IT NOT?

08:25.834 --> 08:28.542
YOU SHOULD NOT BE A DOCTOR.

08:30.792 --> 08:33.417
SO YOU'VE BEEN HAVING
SOME DISCOMFORT?

08:33.458 --> 08:34.917
SORT OF.

08:34.959 --> 08:36.959
WHERE EXACTLY ARE YOU
FEELING PAIN?

08:40.667 --> 08:43.875
I KNOW DISCUSSING THESE THINGS
CAN BE UNCOMFORTABLE.

08:43.917 --> 08:47.750
BUT LET'S SEE IF I CAN HELP?

08:47.792 --> 08:51.375
MY DAUGHTER WAS ATTACKED
BY A MAN.

08:51.417 --> 08:53.542
OH.

08:53.583 --> 08:55.750
I'M SO SORRY.

08:55.792 --> 08:58.041
WHEN DID THIS HAPPEN?

08:58.083 --> 09:00.667
A FEW MONTHS AGO.

09:00.709 --> 09:02.834
AND, UH, IS THIS SOMETHING
THAT YOU REPORTED?

09:02.875 --> 09:06.041
NO.
THAT'S NOT WHAT I WANT.
IT IS NOT SOMETHING WE DO.

09:06.083 --> 09:08.834
BUT IF...
IF YOU WERE RAPED,

09:08.875 --> 09:11.667
SHARBAT, YOU REALLY SHOULD
SPEAK TO SOMEONE.

09:11.709 --> 09:14.667
WE HAVE A PSYCHIATRIST HERE--
THAT'S NOT WHY I CAME HERE.

09:14.709 --> 09:16.041
OKAY.

09:16.083 --> 09:19.458
ARE--ARE YOU STILL FEELING
PAIN FROM THE ATTACK?

09:19.500 --> 09:21.709
THERE IS NO PAIN.

09:21.750 --> 09:23.625
WELL--

09:23.667 --> 09:26.291
NO, PLEASE.

09:26.333 --> 09:29.041
I NEED YOU...

09:29.083 --> 09:31.125
TO MAKE ME
A VIRGIN AGAIN.

09:43.417 --> 09:46.291
YOU CAN MAKE HER VIRGIN AGAIN.
I-I KNOW IT'S POSSIBLE.

09:46.333 --> 09:48.542
IN OUR CULTURE,
SOMETIMES IT IS DONE.

09:48.583 --> 09:50.542
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT
HYMENOPLASTY?

09:50.583 --> 09:53.125
THAT'S NOT SOMETHING
TO BE DONE LIGHTLY.

09:53.166 --> 09:56.959
IT IS A REAL SURGERY WITH
REAL POTENTIAL COMPLICATIONS,

09:57.000 --> 10:00.625
AND AS MUCH
AS WE COULD REPAIR THE HYMEN,

10:00.667 --> 10:02.917
IT DOESN'T MAKE YOU
A VIRGIN.

10:02.959 --> 10:05.083
I AM ENGAGED TO A MAN
IN AFGHANISTAN.

10:05.125 --> 10:07.250
HE WILL TAKE ME AND MY PARENTS
BACK TO OUR COUNTRY,

10:07.291 --> 10:10.333
WHERE WE WILL BE MARRIED,
WHERE HE WILL TAKE CARE OF US.

10:10.375 --> 10:13.417
AND HE DOESN'T KNOW ABOUT
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

10:13.458 --> 10:15.208
I HAVE NOT MET HIM YET.

10:15.250 --> 10:17.834
HE CAN'T KNOW.

10:17.875 --> 10:20.166
HER STATUS, IT...
IT IS CHECKED.

10:20.208 --> 10:23.250
AND ISLAMIC LAW SAYS SEX
BEFORE MARRIAGE IS NOT ALLOWED.

10:23.291 --> 10:25.375
WE WOULD BE DISGRACED.
I UNDERSTAND.

10:25.417 --> 10:28.041
BUT DO YOU UNDERSTAND
THAT WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU

10:28.083 --> 10:30.041
IS NOT YOUR FAULT?

10:30.083 --> 10:33.125
I NEED TO BE PURE.
CAN YOU HELP ME?

10:35.417 --> 10:37.375
COOP, DO YOU THINK
MAYBE WE SHOULD--

10:37.417 --> 10:39.875
SORRY, MAN.
UH, A LITTLE LATER.
OKAY, THIS AFTERNOON THEN.

10:39.917 --> 10:42.875
JUST NEED A COUPLE MINUTES,
BIG GUY. THANKS.
HIS VOTE IS SPOKEN FOR.

10:42.917 --> 10:44.375
IT'S FOR NAOMI.

10:44.417 --> 10:46.875
WAIT, NOTHING'S DECIDED
UNTIL ELECTION DAY, VIOLET.

10:46.917 --> 10:49.875
THIS IS A CAMPAIGN
AB-ABOUT IDEAS. YOU HEAR ME? I--

10:49.917 --> 10:51.375
LOST CAUSE.

10:51.417 --> 10:53.834
NO. NOBODY'S A LOST CAUSE,
EXCEPT FOR MAYBE DELL.

10:53.875 --> 10:55.375
DELL IS A RED STATE.

10:55.417 --> 10:56.834
I'M NOT GETTIN' INVOLVED.

10:56.875 --> 10:59.834
I DID GIVE HIM HIS JOB BACK,
BUT HE AND NAI...

10:59.875 --> 11:02.834
IT'S GONNA BE HARD
TO GET OVER WHAT THEY HAD.

11:02.875 --> 11:04.375
I'M NOT GETTING INVOLVED.

11:04.417 --> 11:06.375
YOU KNOW,
HE QUIT BECAUSE OF HER.

11:06.417 --> 11:09.375
SHOULD I REMIND HIM OF THAT?
I THOUGHT YOU SAID
IT WAS GONNA BE CIVIL.

11:09.417 --> 11:11.667
SO CIVILLY, I'LL REMIND HIM
OF HOW BAD IT WAS.

11:16.333 --> 11:18.291
BAD TIMING, COOP.

11:18.333 --> 11:20.291
BOARD'S GOT A COUPLE
OF BIGWIGS IN,

11:20.333 --> 11:22.291
AND IF I GET ONE MORE COMPLAINT

11:22.333 --> 11:24.291
ABOUT HOW MANY SURGERIES
I SHOULD BE--

11:24.333 --> 11:26.333
I AM NOT IN THE MOOD.

11:26.375 --> 11:30.542
MY DAY'S WORSE. I DON'T FEEL
LIKE HAVING SEX EVER AGAIN.

11:30.583 --> 11:32.542
THEN WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

11:32.583 --> 11:34.583
I CAME TO TALK.

11:39.500 --> 11:42.125
YOU WANTED TO TALK.
YOU'RE NOT TALKING.

11:42.166 --> 11:44.125
DO YOU THINK I'M A PERVERT?

11:44.166 --> 11:47.959
I AM TOO BUSY FOR THIS.
HEY, DOES THIS
NOT BOTHER YOU?

11:48.000 --> 11:49.959
WE'RE BOTH IN THE MIDDLE
OF TOUGH DAYS,

11:50.000 --> 11:53.041
WE CAN'T EVEN DISCUSS IT
WITH ONE ANOTHER?
I DON'T WANT
TO DISCUSS IT, COOPER.

11:53.083 --> 11:56.375
I WANT TO GET THROUGH IT.
MAYBE THAT'S THE DIFFERENCE
BETWEEN YOU AND ME.

11:56.417 --> 11:59.041
I DON'T KNOW
HOW TO GET THROUGH MINE.
WHAT HAPPENED?

11:59.083 --> 12:00.667
A PATIENT'S MOTHER
RECOGNIZED ME

12:00.709 --> 12:02.417
FROM AN ADULT WEB SITE.

12:02.458 --> 12:05.375
SHE DOES NOT WANT ME
TO TREAT HER SON.

12:05.417 --> 12:07.625
THAT'S ABSURD.
YOU DON'T WORRY ABOUT THAT,

12:07.667 --> 12:11.500
A PATIENT RECOGNIZING YOU
FROM YOUR PRIVATE LIFE?
ONE HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH THE OTHER.

12:11.542 --> 12:13.875
BESIDES, I TOOK MINE DOWN.

12:13.917 --> 12:17.041
YOU DIDN'T?

12:17.083 --> 12:20.041
HOW MANY SITES
ARE YOU ON, COOP?

12:20.083 --> 12:21.667
TWO? FIVE?

12:21.709 --> 12:23.834
TEN?
ISH.

12:23.875 --> 12:26.083
YOUR PATIENT MIGHT BE RIGHT.

12:26.125 --> 12:28.417
THERE IS
SOMETHING WRONG WITH YOU.

12:30.458 --> 12:32.166
I'M A GOOD DOCTOR.

12:32.208 --> 12:35.458
