TO ORGANIZE A MALARIA PROGRAM.

17:40.333 --> 17:42.291
OH, THE PETER I REMEMBER
NEVER HESITATED.

17:42.333 --> 17:45.041
HE JUMPED IN
AND DID WHAT NEEDED DOING.

17:45.083 --> 17:47.041
THEN AGAIN,
THE PETER I REMEMBER

17:47.083 --> 17:49.083
