WE WAIT UNTIL THEY COME OUT,

18:12.083 --> 18:15.041
AND THEN WE INTERROGATE HIM
OR HER.
NO, ABOUT MY PATIENT SHARBAT.

18:15.083 --> 18:16.709
SHE LIED.
SHE WASN'T RAPED.

18:16.750 --> 18:19.041
SHE LIED?
