THE SURGERY.

18:37.083 --> 18:39.458
BUT I THOUGHT THAT--
SHE LIED, ADDISON.

18:39.500 --> 18:42.458
IF SHE'S SOME GIRL WHO'S
SLEEPING AROUND AND TELLING LIES

18:42.500 --> 18:45.458
AND MAKING REAL VICTIMS
LOOK BAD, NO, SHE MADE HER BED.

18:45.500 --> 18:49.583
YOU DON'T LIE ABOUT RAPE.
THAT'S ONE OF MY RULES.

19:04.417 --> 19:07.083
NOW THAT'S THE PETER
I REMEMBER.

19:07.125 --> 19:09.041
