ANNULAR LESIONS LIKE THIS.

19:25.583 --> 19:27.542
STOP WORRYING.
IT'S A BITE.

19:27.583 --> 19:29.750
(chuckles)

19:51.583 --> 19:53.625
IT'S AN INSECT BITE,
RIGHT?

19:53.667 --> 19:56.583
WOW. WHAT BIT YOU
AND DID THAT?

19:56.625 --> 19:58.583
I DON'T KNOW.
PROBABLY A SAND FLY.

19:58.625 --> 20:00.875
I'VE BEEN LIVING
IN NIGERIA.

20:00.917 --> 20:02.625
