20:02.667 --> 20:05.375
SO HOW DO YOU KNOW PETE?

20:05.417 --> 20:07.542
WE WERE RESIDENTS TOGETHER.

20:07.583 --> 20:09.875
THEN WE DID
DOCTORS WITHOUT BORDERS

20:09.917 --> 20:11.875
