20:39.041 --> 20:40.250
AMAZING DOCTOR.

20:40.291 --> 20:42.375
WELL, YOU KNOW.

20:42.417 --> 20:44.375
WE'VE ONLY SEEN PETE
DO EASTERN MEDICINE.

20:44.417 --> 20:46.500
