TO GET THE KIDS OUT.

20:58.750 --> 21:01.959
PETER REFUSED TO LEAVE
THE KIDS BEHIND.

21:02.000 --> 21:04.625
HE STAYED WITH 'EM
THROUGH THE NIGHT.

21:04.667 --> 21:08.458
MOST OF THE KIDS SURVIVED
BECAUSE OF HIM.

21:10.542 --> 21:13.083
PETE DID THAT?
OUR PETE?

21:13.125 --> 21:16.500
