"PETE."

21:16.542 --> 21:18.542
TO ME HE WAS ALWAYS "PETER."

21:23.333 --> 21:26.041
PETER.

21:26.083 --> 21:29.041
HEY, YOU GOT A MINUTE?

21:29.083 --> 21:32.041
TO SNOOP ABOUT MEG,
OR HOCK ME FOR A VOTE?

21:32.083 --> 21:35.250
