THIS IS ABOUT THE PRACTICE...

21:35.291 --> 21:37.333
OKAY.
AND THE DIRECTION
THAT IT IS HEADED IN.

21:37.375 --> 21:40.250
NAI--
AND I THINK THAT I CAN SUM UP
EVERYTHING YOU NEED TO KNOW

21:40.291 --> 21:43.041
ABOUT THE DIFFERENCE
BETWEEN SAM AND ME

21:43.083 --> 21:46.542
