PALMILLA, VERY FANCY,

22:31.625 --> 22:33.458
PERFECT, CLEAR BLUE WATERS.

22:33.500 --> 22:36.458
WE COULD GET AWAY.

22:36.500 --> 22:38.041
MM.

22:38.083 --> 22:40.250
(chuckles)

22:40.291 --> 22:42.208
TOO MUCH?
NO. YES.

22:42.250 --> 22:44.417
NO. YE--

22:44.458 --> 22:47.041
YES. (chuckles) NO. HERE--
