WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

23:19.250 --> 23:22.291
(laughs)
I WANT TO KNOW,
BUT, UM, RULES?

23:24.542 --> 23:26.041
SEX RULES.

23:26.083 --> 23:27.500
RULES ABOUT SEX.

23:27.542 --> 23:30.041
YOU KNOW, A HOTEL MEANS
A ROOM, A ROOM MEANS A BED,

23:30.083 --> 23:32.291
