YOU HAVE SEX RULES.

23:32.333 --> 23:35.250
I'M WAITING.
UNTIL MARRIAGE?

23:35.291 --> 23:37.041
NO! NO. (laughs)
(laughs)

23:37.083 --> 23:38.250
NO, NO. I--

23:38.291 --> 23:40.959
JUST TILL, UM...

23:42.375 --> 23:46.041
