UNTIL I'M... SURE.

23:46.083 --> 23:48.208
OKAY.

23:48.250 --> 23:50.333
SO WE'LL WAIT.

23:50.375 --> 23:52.542
I'M GOOD WITH WAITING.

23:52.583 --> 23:54.917
I'M HAPPY WITH WAITING.
REALLY?

23:54.959 --> 23:56.583
