THEY WITHDRAW.

24:46.542 --> 24:49.417
AND THE THING IS,
WITH CORTICOSTEROIDS,

24:49.458 --> 24:51.542
WITH ANTICONVULSANTS,
IT MIGHT BE TREATABLE.

24:51.583 --> 24:55.041
