HOW ABOUT SHADOWING ME THEN?

25:40.417 --> 25:42.333
YEAH. THAT WOULD BE NICE.
THANK YOU. THANK YOU.

25:42.375 --> 25:45.250
LOOK, DELL, I KNOW
WE'VE HAD A DIFFICULT PATCH,

25:45.291 --> 25:47.250
BUT WE HAVE A HISTORY.

25:47.291 --> 25:50.333
AND, UH, I HOPE YOU KNOW
HOW IMPORTANT YOU ARE TO ME

25:50.375 --> 25:53.917
AND TO THE PRACTICE.
(Sam) THOUGH I'M THE ONE
WHO GAVE YOU YOUR JOB BACK.

25:53.959 --> 25:56.917
YEAH, WELL,
AFTER I BEGGED YOU TO.
EXCUSE ME.

25:56.959 --> 25:58.917
DELL, I KNOW
THAT YOU'RE THE PERSON

25:58.959 --> 26:00.750
THAT KEEPS
THIS PRACTICE RUNNING.

26:00.792 --> 26:03.041
AND I UNDERSTAND THAT YOU
WANT TO BE DOING MORE.
UH-HUH.

26:03.083 --> 26:05.458
AND I THINK YOU SHOULD.
I THINK YOU'RE READY FOR IT,

26:05.500 --> 26:07.458
READY FOR MORE
THAN JUST "SHADOWING."
SAM.

26:07.500 --> 26:09.458
YEAH.
UH, DELL AND I
WERE TALKING, SO--

26:09.500 --> 26:11.458
OH, I'M SORRY. ALL RIGHT. WELL,
WHEN YOU'RE DONE WITH ALL--

26:11.500 --> 26:13.709
STOP BY MY OFFICE FOR A FEW,
ALL RIGHT?
OKAY.

26:13.750 --> 26:16.500
YOU KNOW WHAT?
SAM DOESN'T CARE ABOUT YOU.

26:16.542 --> 26:18.500
ALL HE CARES ABOUT
IS THE BOTTOM LINE.

26:18.542 --> 26:19.834
OH, WELL, YOU'VE SEEN

26:19.875 --> 26:22.208
WHAT THE BOTTOM LINE
WITH NAOMI IS, RIGHT?

26:22.250 --> 26:24.291
YOU KEEP HER SECRETS,
YOU HIDE HER MISTAKES,

26:24.333 --> 26:27.041
THEN YOU JUST WAIT
FOR THE AX TO DROP.
YOU KNOW WHAT?

26:27.083 --> 26:29.500
SAM DOESN'T CARE ABOUT WHAT
THIS PLACE IS SUPPOSED TO BE.
WELL, THIS PLACE WOULDN'T BE
ANYTHING BUT BROKE

26:29.542 --> 26:33.250
IF SHE'S RUNNING THINGS.
IS THIS HOW YOU EXPECT
TO GET MY VOTE?

26:33.291 --> 26:35.041
♪♪

26:35.083 --> 26:37.083
YOU CAN'T CHANGE WHAT YOU DID.

26:37.125 --> 26:40.542
YOU KNOW, AND WE CAN'T LIVE
WITH WHAT YOU'RE DOING.
WHY ARE YOU FIGHTING WITH ME?

26:40.583 --> 26:42.542
I'M MAKING PROGRESS HERE,
ALL RIGHT?

26:42.583 --> 26:45.417
I'M GETTING US
UP OUT OF THIS HOLE.
YOU KNOW WHAT?
BECAUSE PEOPLE AREN'T HAPPY.

26:45.458 --> 26:47.041
PEOPLE AREN'T HAPPY,

26:47.083 --> 26:49.834
OR YOU'RE NOT HAPPY
BECAUSE IT'S NOT YOUR WAY?
MY WAY?

26:49.875 --> 26:52.041
WELL, THAT'S WHAT IT ALL
COMES DOWN TO, RIGHT?
AT LEAST I HAVE A WAY...

26:52.083 --> 26:54.959
DEMOCRACY IN ACTION.
WHY DON'T YOU JUST ADMIT IT?

26:55.000 --> 26:56.875
I'M THE ONE WHO DID
EVERYTHING IN THE BEGINNING!

27:01.083 --> 27:02.542
I THINK LIES ARE CONTAGIOUS.

27:02.583 --> 27:05.000
PETE NOT TELLING US
ABOUT HIS PAST IS NOT A LIE.

27:05.041 --> 27:07.000
IT'S AN OMISSION.
FINE, THAT'S ONE THING.

27:07.041 --> 27:09.000
YOU LIED ABOUT CHARLOTTE.
I TOLD YOU.

27:09.041 --> 27:12.000
AND NOW I HAVE TO NOT TELL
EVERYBODY ELSE. THAT'S A LIE.

27:12.041 --> 27:13.291
SAM?

27:13.333 --> 27:15.792
SECRETLY SLEEPING
WITH NAOMI.

27:15.834 --> 27:17.959
LIE. LIE.
DELL?

27:18.000 --> 27:20.291
KEPT NAOMI'S SECRET.
OMISSION. LIE.

27:20.333 --> 27:21.458
ADDISON?

27:21.500 --> 27:23.458
WELL, HER PATIENT LIED
ABOUT BEING RAPED.

27:23.500 --> 27:25.917
OH.
BUT I GUESS I CAN'T
HOLD THAT AGAINST HER.

27:25.959 --> 27:27.458
YOU KNOW WHAT, ADDISON?

27:27.500 --> 27:30.500
YOU MAY BE THE ONLY ONE HERE
THAT'S TRUSTWORTHY.
LOW BAR.

27:36.417 --> 27:39.792
DO YOU REALLY THINK
YOU CAN HELP HIM?

27:39.834 --> 27:41.792
IF WE GIVE BRADEN
PREDNISONE NOW,

27:41.834 --> 27:43.792
IT'LL ABSORB
INTO HIS BLOODSTREAM

27:43.834 --> 27:45.834
IN A MATTER OF HOURS.

27:45.875 --> 27:49.792
BEFORE HE GOES TO BED,
WE COULD KNOW IF IT'LL HELP.

27:53.583 --> 27:55.709
DID YOU REALLY
WORK IN AFRICA

27:55.750 --> 27:58.625
TREATING KIDS
WITH RIVER BLINDNESS?

27:58.667 --> 28:01.250
HAVE YOU HEARD THE STORY ABOUT
HIM AND THE BOSNIAN ORPHANS?
NO!

28:01.291 --> 28:03.291
WHERE DID YOU
HEAR ABOUT THAT?
IN THE LADIES ROOM.

28:03.333 --> 28:05.291
WHAT DO YOU PEOPLE
DO IN THERE?

28:05.333 --> 28:08.208
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL US
YOU HAD THIS WHOLE PAST, PETE?
PETER.

28:08.250 --> 28:10.083
PETER?

28:10.125 --> 28:13.000
IT WAS A LONG TIME AGO.

28:15.583 --> 28:18.166
YOU REALLY LIKE HER.

28:24.083 --> 28:26.625
LOOK...

28:26.667 --> 28:28.792
SHARBAT...

28:28.834 --> 28:31.792
I KNOW YOU WANT THIS.
YOU THINK YOU WANT THIS.

28:31.834 --> 28:34.041
IT'S THE ONLY WAY.
IT MAY BE THE ONLY WAY

28:34.083 --> 28:37.375
FOR THIS MAN YOU'RE SUPPOSED
TO MARRY, BUT FOR YOU--

28:37.417 --> 28:39.667
YOU NEED TO FIGURE OUT
WHAT'S RIGHT FOR YOU.

28:39.709 --> 28:42.208
LOOK, YOU TOLD YOUR MOTHER
ABOUT THE RAPE.

28:42.250 --> 28:45.417
TELL HER ABOUT THIS BOY
YOU LOVE.

28:45.458 --> 28:47.417
DO YOU REALLY WANT
YOUR FUTURE

28:47.458 --> 28:50.041
TO BE BASED ON A LIE?

28:55.083 --> 28:57.792
HAVE YOU BEEN HAVING FATIGUE,
HEADACHE, JOINT PAINS?

28:57.834 --> 29:00.375
I'VE BEEN ON AND OFF AIRPLANES
ALL MONTH

29:00.417 --> 29:02.291
IN HALF A DOZEN
DIFFERENT TIME ZONES.

29:02.333 --> 29:04.250
Y-YES, I HAVE.

29:04.291 --> 29:06.250
OH, COME ON, SAM.
WHAT IS IT?

29:06.291 --> 29:09.000
THERE WE GO.

29:09.041 --> 29:10.500
THIS.

29:10.542 --> 29:12.542
THAT WAS IN MY BACK?

29:12.583 --> 29:14.750
YEAH. IT'S THE REMNANTS
OF A TICK.

29:14.792 --> 29:17.041
PROBABLY BEEN IN THERE
A WEEK OR SO.

29:17.083 --> 29:18.291
PETE WAS RIGHT.

29:18.333 --> 29:20.291
THESE THINGS CAN CAUSE
A NASTY INFECTION.

29:20.333 --> 29:23.041
IF YOU WOULD'VE LET IT
LAST ANY LONGER,

29:23.083 --> 29:25.291
YOU COULD HAVE WOUND UP
WITH SERIOUS CARDIAC PROBLEMS,

29:25.333 --> 29:27.041
ENCEPHALITIS--

29:27.083 --> 29:28.250
WELL, THANK YOU.

29:28.291 --> 29:31.041
WELL, YOU CAN THANK PETER.

29:31.083 --> 29:33.333
I DON'T SUPPOSE I COULD
PAY YOU OFF

29:33.375 --> 29:36.417
TO SAY IT WAS
A SAND FLY BITE?

29:36.458 --> 29:37.875
(laughs)

29:42.000 --> 29:45.000
OH. (exhales slowly)

29:46.834 --> 29:48.458
YOU DECIDE WHAT TO DO?

29:48.500 --> 29:51.375
I DECIDED THE TRUTH
SEEMED BETTER.

29:51.417 --> 29:54.959
HEY, SPEAKING OF WHICH, UH,

29:55.000 --> 29:58.041
WHY IS IT THAT NO ONE SEEMS
TO KNOW ANYTHING ABOUT YOU?

29:58.083 --> 30:02.041
YOU KNOW ME.
APPARENTLY WE DON'T EVEN
KNOW YOUR NAME... PETER.

30:02.083 --> 30:05.291
LOOK, THE PAST IS THE PAST.
I'M NOT ONE TO DWELL ON IT.

30:05.333 --> 30:09.500
BUT MEG--SHE SEEMS LIKE
A GOOD PART OF YOUR PAST.

30:09.542 --> 30:12.250
SHE'S HERE NOW.
THEN SHE'LL BE GONE.

30:12.291 --> 30:14.959
SO... IT IS WHAT IT IS.

30:15.041 --> 30:16.500
UNLESS IT ISN'T.

30:16.542 --> 30:18.959
YOU COULD NOT LET HER GO.

30:19.000 --> 30:21.000
YOU KNOW WHAT YOUR PROBLEM IS?

30:21.041 --> 30:23.041
YOU ARE A ROMANTIC.

30:23.083 --> 30:25.291
YOU DON'T WANT THEM
RUNNING THIS PLACE TOGETHER.

30:25.333 --> 30:28.000
YOU WANT THEM TOGETHER--
SAM AND NAOMI THE WAY IT WAS,

30:28.041 --> 30:30.000
YOU AND NAOMI
THE WAY IT WAS.

30:30.041 --> 30:33.750
WHAT'S WRONG WITH THAT?
I LIKE THE WAY IT WAS.

30:33.792 --> 30:34.959
(door opens)

30:47.083 --> 30:49.542
THANK YOU.

30:49.583 --> 30:52.208
WHAT SHARBAT
IS ASKING FOR,

30:52.250 --> 30:55.250
WHAT SHE WANTS TO GIVE UP
IS A LOT.

30:55.291 --> 30:59.041
AND I THOUGHT
YOU SHOULD KNOW THE TRUTH.

30:59.083 --> 31:01.875
I KNEW.
MOTHERS ARE MOTHERS.

31:01.917 --> 31:04.792
WHAT SHE COULDN'T TELL ME,
I KNEW.
I'M SORRY.
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

31:04.834 --> 31:07.792
YOU LET HER SAY
SHE WAS RAPED?
IF SHE BROKE THE TRUST

31:07.834 --> 31:11.000
THAT HER FATHER AND I HAVE
IN HER, IT WOULD BE HER SIN.

31:11.041 --> 31:13.000
SHE WOULD HAVE FELT SHAME.

31:13.041 --> 31:16.000
IT WAS EASIER FOR HER TO SAY
IT WAS SOMEONE ELSE'S.

31:16.041 --> 31:18.458
WE'VE TALKED.

31:18.500 --> 31:20.458
NOW WILL YOU DO
THE SURGERY?

31:20.500 --> 31:22.583
UH...

31:24.208 --> 31:26.208
SHARBAT,
NO MATTER WHAT I DO,

31:26.250 --> 31:29.041
I CAN'T MAKE YOU FORGET
WHAT YOU HAD HERE.

31:29.083 --> 31:31.834
I LOVE MY PARENTS MORE
THAN ANYTHING IN THIS WORLD.

31:31.875 --> 31:34.250
I JUST WANT
TO TAKE THEM HOME.

31:34.291 --> 31:36.250
PLEASE, IF I DON'T BURY
MY PAST,

31:36.291 --> 31:38.500
MY FAMILY WILL HAVE
NO FUTURE.

31:44.208 --> 31:46.250
NO, NO, NO,
I'LL TELL YOU WHAT--
STOP, STOP TALKING.

31:46.291 --> 31:48.250
JUST LISTEN--LISTEN TO
WHAT I'M SAYING.
WAIT, NO, NO, NO.
I'M GONNA TELL YOU WHAT.

31:48.291 --> 31:51.041
YOU GOT ME OUT OF THE MARRIAGE.
NOW WHAT YOU CAN DO

31:51.083 --> 31:53.458
IS YOU AN ADDISON CAN GO AHEAD
AND TAKE OVER THE PRACTICE.
FOR THE LAST TIME--
PROBABLY NOT THE LAST TIME...

31:53.500 --> 31:55.917
MAYBE I'LL GO WORK
OVER AT ST. AMBROSE.
BECAUSE WE'LL PROBABLY HAVE THIS
ARGUMENT MAYBE NINE MORE TIMES

31:55.959 --> 31:58.667
BEFORE THE END OF THE DAY...
NO, REALLY, I'M SURE THAT I
COULD FIND A JOB THERE...

31:58.709 --> 32:01.041
SINCE WE'VE ALREADY HAD IT
THREE TIMES. ADDISON--
IF YOU DON'T MIND, WE'RE TRYING
TO HAVE A PRIVATE CONVERSATION.

32:01.083 --> 32:02.667
I DON'T CARE.

32:02.709 --> 32:04.000
GREAT.

32:10.792 --> 32:13.041
LOOK, MAYBE THIS IS MY FAULT.

32:13.083 --> 32:15.959
I PUSHED US TO TRY
TO RECAPTURE THE PAST,

32:16.000 --> 32:19.250
WHAT WE HAD,
WHAT THIS PLACE USED TO BE.

32:19.291 --> 32:22.250
BUT THE PAST IS CLUTTERED
WITH ANGER AND MISTAKES,

32:22.291 --> 32:24.208
AND WE NEED TO BURY THAT.

32:24.250 --> 32:27.417
IT DOESN'T MATTER
WHO DID WHAT WHEN.

32:27.458 --> 32:29.208
IT MATTERS
WHAT WE WANT TO DO NOW,

32:29.250 --> 32:31.834
WHAT WE WANT THIS PLACE
TO BE GOING FORWARD.

32:31.875 --> 32:34.875
WE NEED TO FOCUS ON PATIENTS,
AND WE NEED TO EARN MONEY.

32:34.917 --> 32:37.291
WE NEED NAOMI AND WE NEED SAM,

32:37.333 --> 32:39.500
THE BEST OF BOTH OF YOU.

32:39.542 --> 32:41.500
AND THIS VOTE,
IT'S A BAD IDEA,

32:41.542 --> 32:44.125
AN IDEA THAT WE MIGHT NEVER
RECOVER FROM.

32:44.166 --> 32:46.083
WE SHOULDN'T DO IT.

32:46.125 --> 32:48.750
LET'S SIT DOWN AND FIGURE OUT

32:48.792 --> 32:51.542
WHAT WE WANT
THIS PLACE TO BE, TOGETHER.

32:51.583 --> 32:53.542
IF YOU FORCE US TO CHOOSE
BETWEEN YOU,

32:53.583 --> 32:57.125
THAT WILL CREATE SCARS
THAT WON'T HEAL.

32:57.166 --> 33:00.500
WE NEED TO MOVE FORWARD,
NOT BACK.

33:09.083 --> 33:11.500
WE VOTE
AT THE END OF THE DAY.

33:11.542 --> 33:13.083
(sighs)

33:27.375 --> 33:30.333
(monitor beeping rhythmically)

33:33.333 --> 33:35.208
SHARBAT...

33:35.250 --> 33:37.417
ARE YOU READY?

33:37.458 --> 33:39.542
HE'S JUST A BOY.

33:39.583 --> 33:41.625
HE'S A NICE BOY,

33:41.667 --> 33:45.041
BUT WE WOULD NOT LAST.

33:45.083 --> 33:48.458
HE'S YOUNG,
HE'S GOT COLLEGE,

33:48.500 --> 33:51.125
HE'S SO AMERICAN.

33:51.166 --> 33:54.834
HE'S NOT MY FUTURE.

33:54.875 --> 33:57.041
I WANT TO DO THIS.

33:57.083 --> 34:00.458
SO, YES, I AM READY.

34:28.291 --> 34:31.834
DOC... TOR?

34:36.959 --> 34:41.250
THANK YOU...
FOR THE TRUCK.

34:41.291 --> 34:43.709
(chuckles) YOU'RE WELCOME.

34:46.959 --> 34:49.250
(voice breaking)
HE STARTED 45 MINUTES AGO.

34:49.291 --> 34:51.542
HE WOKE UP.

34:51.583 --> 34:55.333
WHATEVER YOU ARE,
YOU ARE A WONDERFUL DOCTOR.

35:11.500 --> 35:14.000
SO WE'RE REALLY
GONNA DO THIS?

35:20.083 --> 35:22.500
I'M NOT VOTING.
I WON'T BE PART OF THIS.

35:30.583 --> 35:34.083
WELL, LET'S JUST--LET'S COUNT
THE VOTES WE HAVE.

35:34.125 --> 35:36.291
SAM. (clears throat)

35:36.333 --> 35:38.500
NAOMI.

35:43.291 --> 35:45.208
ADDISON.

35:47.375 --> 35:51.000
OKAY, WHOEVER DID THAT,
IT IS NOT FUNNY.

35:51.041 --> 35:53.291
ADDISON.

35:53.333 --> 35:56.000
ADDISON.

35:56.041 --> 35:58.250
ADDISON.

36:04.083 --> 36:07.041
NO. NO, NO, NO, NO,
NO, NO, NO.

36:07.083 --> 36:09.000
NO. NO.

36:11.083 --> 36:12.792
NICE SPEECH.

36:12.834 --> 36:15.333
IT WON MY VOTE.

36:15.375 --> 36:17.625
CONGRATULATIONS, BOSS.

36:19.792 --> 36:22.125
EVEN YOU VOTED FOR ME?

36:22.166 --> 36:24.125
IF EITHER ONE OF THEM
HAD WON,

36:24.166 --> 36:26.250
THIS PLACE STILL
WOULD HAVE BEEN DIVIDED.

36:26.291 --> 36:28.000
OH.

36:30.375 --> 36:33.041
WHAT AM I
SUPPOSED TO DO NOW?

36:33.083 --> 36:35.417
FIGURE OUT
WHAT THE FUTURE IS.

36:35.458 --> 36:37.333
FIGURE OUT
WHAT THE NEW RULES ARE.

36:37.375 --> 36:40.166
YOU THINK RULES REALLY WORK?

36:40.208 --> 36:43.041
SO LONG AS YOU REMEMBER
THEY'RE MEANT TO BE BROKEN.

36:43.083 --> 36:45.417
HEY, VIOLET...

36:45.458 --> 36:48.375
ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED
IN YOUR OFFICE--

36:48.417 --> 36:51.750
I DON'T--I DON'T
WANT TO TALK ABOUT THAT.
ARE YOU SURE?

36:51.792 --> 36:53.834
YEAH. WE'RE NOT--WE'RE NOT
GOING THERE, ADDISON.

36:53.875 --> 36:55.417
IT IS WHAT IT IS.

37:01.333 --> 37:04.125
(exhales deeply)

37:17.709 --> 37:20.458
I'M SORRY, NAOMI.

37:23.083 --> 37:27.041
IF I COULD GO BACK
AND CHANGE WHAT I DID...

37:27.083 --> 37:29.041
HOW I TREATED YOU...

37:29.083 --> 37:32.417
I MESSED UP.

37:32.458 --> 37:35.250
I'M SORRY.

37:49.333 --> 37:52.333
♪♪

38:03.458 --> 38:06.667
♪♪

38:17.625 --> 38:20.959
♪♪

38:23.417 --> 38:25.125
THANK YOU...

38:25.166 --> 38:27.542
FOR WORRYING ABOUT ME.

38:27.583 --> 38:29.709
♪♪

38:29.750 --> 38:32.250
YOU KNOW, I REALLY COULD
USE YOU IN GHANA.

38:32.291 --> 38:34.709
DON'T YOU REMEMBER
WHAT IT WAS LIKE?

38:34.750 --> 38:37.709
NO MATTER WHAT GODFORSAKEN
PART OF THE WORLD WE WERE IN,

38:37.750 --> 38:41.208
NO MATTER WHAT DISASTER
OR DISEASE WE WERE FIGHTING,

38:41.250 --> 38:45.041
PEOPLE ALWAYS
RESPONDED TO YOU.

38:45.083 --> 38:46.709
THAT'S A GIFT.

38:46.750 --> 38:48.709
DON'T WASTE IT HERE.

38:48.750 --> 38:50.709
I'M PART OF SOMETHING
I BELIEVE IN--

38:50.750 --> 38:53.583
BUILDING IT, MAKING IT WORK.

38:53.625 --> 38:55.125
I LIKE IT HERE.

38:55.166 --> 38:57.625
♪♪

38:57.667 --> 38:59.542
I ALSO LIKE YOU HERE.

38:59.583 --> 39:02.375
♪♪

39:02.417 --> 39:04.291
YEAH,
EXCEPT FOR THE SMOKING.

39:04.333 --> 39:07.792
I FORGOT YOU CAME
WITH CIGARETTES.

39:07.834 --> 39:11.041
SO IS THAT AN INVITATION?

39:11.083 --> 39:14.417
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

39:14.458 --> 39:17.083
BUT YOU GOTTA QUIT SMOKING.

39:17.125 --> 39:19.834
I DON'T CHANGE
FOR ANYONE.

39:19.875 --> 39:23.417
♪♪

39:27.917 --> 39:30.125
(laughs)

39:30.166 --> 39:34.333
NICE OUTFIT, FRAULEIN.

39:34.375 --> 39:36.041
♪♪

39:36.083 --> 39:38.792
GET OVER HERE.

39:38.834 --> 39:40.333
NO.

39:40.375 --> 39:42.458
♪♪

39:42.500 --> 39:45.458
DO I LOOK LIKE A PERSON
WHO TAKES NO FOR AN ANSWER?

39:45.500 --> 39:47.500
I WOULD VERY MUCH LIKE IT

39:47.542 --> 39:49.667
IF WE COULD SPEND
THE EVENING... TALKING.

39:49.709 --> 39:51.375
AGAIN WITH THE TALKING?

39:51.417 --> 39:55.041
I'M SERIOUS. WE'RE GONNA
GET TO KNOW EACH OTHER.
WHY?

39:55.083 --> 39:56.417
BECAUSE, HERR CHARLOTTE,

39:56.458 --> 39:59.083
I WANT US TO BE
ABOUT MORE THAN SEX,

39:59.125 --> 40:01.875
BECAUSE I WANT TO KNOW YOU
AND YOU TO KNOW ME,

40:01.917 --> 40:03.792
LIKE NORMAL PEOPLE.

40:03.834 --> 40:06.375
♪♪

40:06.417 --> 40:07.834
(clears throat)

40:07.875 --> 40:09.458
FOR INSTANCE, ME.

40:09.500 --> 40:11.792
I'M FROM AKRON.

40:11.834 --> 40:13.792
I'M AN ONLY CHILD.

40:13.834 --> 40:16.250
I WAS ADOPTED,
AND I NEVER CARED.

40:16.291 --> 40:18.834
I NEVER SOUGHT OUT
MY BIRTH PARENTS

40:18.875 --> 40:21.041
BECAUSE MY PARENTS WERE GREAT,
ARE GREAT.

40:21.083 --> 40:24.333
AND, UH, I SPENT SUMMERS
WORKING AT A CAMP IN INDIANA,

40:24.375 --> 40:27.041
WHICH IS WHEN I REALIZED
THAT I LOVED CHILDREN

40:27.083 --> 40:32.041
AND, UH, DECIDED I WANTED
TO BE A PEDIATRICIAN.

40:32.083 --> 40:35.625
MY FAVORITE COLOR
IS CHARTREUSE

40:35.667 --> 40:38.083
BECAUSE I LIKE
THE WAY IT SOUNDS

40:38.125 --> 40:41.041
COMING OUT OF MY MOUTH--
CHARTREUSE.

40:41.083 --> 40:43.041
♪♪

40:43.083 --> 40:44.125
CHARTREUSE.

40:44.166 --> 40:46.333
CHARTREUSE.

40:46.375 --> 40:49.542
♪♪

40:51.792 --> 40:54.291
THAT IS A GOOD WORD.

40:56.542 --> 41:00.417
OKAY, NOW IT'S YOUR TURN.
(clears throat)

41:00.458 --> 41:03.959
♪♪

41:04.000 --> 41:06.875
WELL... UM...

41:06.917 --> 41:10.333
I'M FROM
MONROEVILLE, ALABAMA...

41:10.375 --> 41:12.750
(chuckles)
HOME OF HARPER LEE,

41:12.792 --> 41:14.250
WHO WROTE--

41:14.291 --> 41:16.250
"TO KILL A MOCKINGBIRD."

41:16.291 --> 41:18.125
RIGHT.

41:18.166 --> 41:20.041
♪♪

41:20.083 --> 41:22.500
WHICH IS MY FAVORITE BOOK.

41:22.542 --> 41:24.250
YES, I READ.

41:24.291 --> 41:25.750
(laughs)

41:25.792 --> 41:29.333
♪♪

41:31.542 --> 41:33.166
HEY.
HEY.

41:33.208 --> 41:37.375
♪♪

41:37.417 --> 41:39.041
I'M GLAD YOU CALLED.

41:39.083 --> 41:41.291
YEAH.

41:41.333 --> 41:44.333
(clears throat)

41:44.375 --> 41:48.333
♪♪

42:02.834 --> 42:06.000
♪♪

